3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the problem of limited knowledge in packet processing, which is related to information theory. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with managing queues in a system, which is a topic covered in this sub-category. 
5. cs.PF (Performance) - The paper analyzes the performance of the proposed algorithm, which is a key topic in this sub-category.
